      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2023 R1 is a commercially validated solver with documented V&V reports and ISO 9001 quality management. FDA-internal Ansys installation is controlled under OSEL software QA procedures. DePuy Synthes FEA team operates under a design-control SOP aligned with 21 CFR Part 820. All three modeling teams demonstrated achievedLevel 3."
