      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture constraints: fixed inferior block, superior block loaded in compression-bending at 10-degree offset. Screw-rod assembly torque, intervertebral distance (44 mm), and screw angulation (0 degrees) matched between model and test. Equivalency table documented in the V&V report appendix."
