      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric per ASME V&V 40 Section 5. Validation uncertainty (uval) computed from experimental standard deviation and model parameter uncertainty via Monte Carlo propagation (N=1000 samples). All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion."
